@2    = ~Ribald's Flute of Genie Summoning~
@3    = ~When played, this flute allows you to summon Ribald's genie for the express purpose of being transported to the Adventurers Mart. Many of Ribald's regular customers, spread out across faerun, were tired of long travels to their favourite store. So Ribald commanded the genie he had captured on one of his adventures to transport anyone playing one of these flutes to his store.

STATISTICS

Once per day a genie can be summoned to transport the party to the Adventurers Mart and back.~
